headline: Chickens are becoming 3rd most popular pet: Tractor Supply CEO
summary: Tractor Supply Company (TSCO) is expecting high demand for its live chick and chicken sales through the chain's Chick Days promotions. Tractor Supply Company CEO Hal Lawton talks about his company's chicken sales as rising egg prices have been a concerning economic indicator throughout 2025.
